#README - GVSU Libraries UI Pattern Library

---

This tool was developed by Matthew Reidsma to make it easy to design new web projects at GVSU Libraries while maintaining a consistent look and feel to the user interface. We hope you find it useful.

INSTALLATION

You can run the file locally or on a server. Feel free to adapt the styles in css/libui.css to match your institutions branding, and update the full path of the file in line 66 to match your server.

More questions? Feel free to contact Matthew Reidsma on Twitter at @mreidsma or via email at reidsmam@gvsu.edu.

DEMO

You can view a live version of this tool at http://gvsu.edu/library/ui.

